# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Google Places API (Server-Only, Optional)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# To enable Google Reviews feature:
# 1. Create API key: https://console.cloud.google.com/apis/credentials
# 2. Enable: Places API (New)
# 3. Find your Place ID: https://developers.google.com/maps/documentation/places/web-service/place-id
#
# Leave empty to disable Google Reviews (app works without it)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=your_google_places_api_key_here
GOOGLE_PLACE_ID=your_google_place_id_here

# For STAGING: Set in GitHub Secrets as:
#   STAGING_GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY
#   STAGING_GOOGLE_PLACE_ID

# For PRODUCTION: Set in GitHub Secrets as:
#   PRODUCTION_GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY
#   PRODUCTION_GOOGLE_PLACE_ID

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Environment-Specific Configuration Guide
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# LOCAL DEVELOPMENT (.env.local)
# ==============================
# File: .env.local (gitignored, never committed)
# Supabase: Local instance (npx supabase start)
# Purpose: Feature development and testing
# Commands:
#   npx supabase start     # Start local Supabase
#   npm run dev            # Start Next.js dev server
#   npm run test:routes    # Test routes locally

# STAGING (GitHub Secrets + GCP)
# ===============================
# Branch: develop
# Deployment: Automatic on push to develop
# Cloud Run: cfb-website-staging
# Supabase: Staging project (create at supabase.com)
# GitHub Secrets:
#   STAGING_SUPABASE_URL
#   STAGING_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
#   STAGING_SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY
#   STAGING_GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY (optional)
#   STAGING_GOOGLE_PLACE_ID (optional)
# GCP Secrets:
#   staging-supabase-url
#   staging-supabase-anon-key
#   staging-supabase-service-role-key
#   staging-google-places-api-key (optional)
#   staging-google-place-id (optional)
# Commands:
#   git push origin develop  # Deploy to staging

# PRODUCTION (GitHub Secrets + GCP)
# ==================================
# Branch: main
# Deployment: Automatic on push to main
# Cloud Run: cfb-website
# Supabase: Production project (create at supabase.com)
# GitHub Secrets:
#   PRODUCTION_SUPABASE_URL
#   PRODUCTION_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
#   PRODUCTION_SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY
#   PRODUCTION_GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY (optional)
#   PRODUCTION_GOOGLE_PLACE_ID (optional)
# GCP Secrets:
#   production-supabase-url
#   production-supabase-anon-key
#   production-supabase-service-role-key
#   production-google-places-api-key (optional)
#   production-google-place-id (optional)
# Commands:
#   git push origin main  # Deploy to production

